- So why are people still dying?
- In my opinion, the problem is not access to treatment.
This is my opinion, and so it is in our hospital.
At least in the past 12 years we have had no supply problems with the medications. The problem is that people come into a very advanced state because they do not know their state of infection, i.e. in very late stages of the disease.
