This proposal is approved by the professionals and officials of the Consejo Estatal de Prevención del Sida en Jalisco (Coesida) (State Committee on AIDS Prevention in Jalisco) and also by the patients such as Fabrizio, who had his test carried out in a private laboratory, and this for the sole reason that it had even made a friend of him who, despite his young age, was a common turcoma and phase of AIDS.
